{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"touchcancel","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/touchcancel_event","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><code style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: inherit;\">touchcancel</code><span style=\"line-height: inherit;\">&nbsp;이벤트는 &nbsp;터치포인트가 현재 구현된 방식안에서 방해 받을때 ( 예를들어 너무 많은 터치 포인트) &nbsp;발생한다.</span></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"general_info","title":"General info","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"specification\">Specification</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\"><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/touch-events/#the-touchcancel-event\" rel=\" noopener\">Touch Events</a></dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">TouchEvent</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Yes</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">No</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">Document, Element</dd>\n <dt style=\"float: left; text-align: right; width: 120px;\" id=\"default_action\">Default Action</dt>\n <dd style=\"margin: 0 0 0 120px;\">None</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"properties","title":"Properties","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>EventTarget</td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>DOMString</td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>Boolean</td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>Boolean</td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>view</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>WindowProxy</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/defaultView\" title=\"In browsers, document.defaultView returns the window object associated with a document, or null if none is available.\"><code>document.defaultView</code></a> (<code>window</code> of the document)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>detail</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>long (float)</td>\n   <td>0.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>touches</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>TouchList</td>\n   <td>A list of <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Touch\"><code>Touch</code></a>es for every point of contact currently touching the surface.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>targetTouches</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>TouchList</td>\n   <td>A list of <a href=\"/en-US/DOM/Touch\"><code>Touch</code></a>es for every point of contact that is touching the surface and started on the element that is the target of the current event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>changedTouches</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>TouchList</td>\n   <td>A list of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch\"><code>Touch</code></a>es for every point of contact which contributed to the event.<br>\n    For the touchstart event this must be a list of the touch points that just became active with the current event. For the touchmove event this must be a list of the touch points that have moved since the last event. For the touchend and touchcancel events this must be a list of the touch points that have just been removed from the surface.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>ctrlKey</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the control key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>shiftKey</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the shift key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>altKey</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the alt key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>metaKey</code> <span title=\"This value may not be changed.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Read only </span></td>\n   <td>boolean</td>\n   <td><code>true</code> if the meta key was down when the event was fired. <code>false</code> otherwise.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>해당 이벤트의 샘플코드는&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Touch_events\" style=\"line-height: inherit;\">Touch events</a>&nbsp;에서 확인할 수 있다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"related_events","title":"Related Events","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchstart_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">touchstart (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchend_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">touchend (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/touchmove_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">touchmove (en-US)</a></code></li>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/touchcancel_event\" title=\"/ko/docs/Web/Reference/Events/touchcancel\">touchcancel</a></code></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"General info","id":"general_info"},{"text":"Properties","id":"properties"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Related Events","id":"related_events"}],"summary":"touchcancel 이벤트는  터치포인트가 현재 구현된 방식안에서 방해 받을때 ( 예를들어 너무 많은 터치 포인트)  발생한다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Element: touchcancel event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Element: touchcancel event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"touchcancel","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"touchcancel","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/element/touchcancel_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/element/touchcancel_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element","title":"Element"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/Element/touchcancel_event","title":"touchcancel"}],"pageTitle":"touchcancel - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}